title: Goat's cheese and asparagus tart
ingredients: ['500g puff pastry', "225g goat's cheese", '12 asparagus spears', '6 tablespoons olive oil', '1 red onion, finely chopped', '2 cloves garlic, minced', '1 teaspoon cumin seeds', 'juice of 1/2 lemon', '1 teaspoon corainder seeds', 'salt and pepper, to taste', 'grated Parmesan cheese, to taste']
